Merge branch 'alex/mut-ref-to-reproducible-rng' into 'master'

chore(crypto): CRP-2087 take mutable reference to RNG

Instead of binding mutably to the owned object and taking a mutable reference when needed
```
let mut rng = reproducible_rng();
f1(&mut rng);
f2(&mut rng);
...
```
use the shorter syntax by binding to a mutable reference as
```
let rng = &mut reproducible_rng();
f1(rng);
f2(rng);
``` 

